name: FRESHENER AIRE 3000 SHOT COOL LINEN
description: Air Freshener. Odor-neutralizing system—eliminates bad odors. Compact concentrated scent refills deliver the finest spray mist for more noticeable, long-lasting performance. Tailored dispensing capabilities make this system the most sophisticated air freshening system available. Microburst 3000 models feature programming abilities; LED model is fully programmable —choose start/stop times, day of week setting and frequency of bursts. Economizer model features a compact design for smaller areas with time programming capabilities for 15, 30 or 60 minutes between bursts; LumeCel™ is a rechargeable energy system. Standard Aerosol features adjustable spray intervals from 5 to 25 minutes; Low refill and battery indicators.
